message:
Task complete. I implemented and tested the solution:

- /workspace/solution.py — final program (reads N from stdin, prints count of integers ≤ N with exactly 9 divisors).
- /workspace/eval_test.py — brute-force test harness (used for exhaustive checks up to 5000).
- /workspace/evaluation.txt — evaluation scores and reasoning.

Verification performed: sample tests (N=200 → 3; N=4_000_000_000_000 → 407073) and exhaustive checks up to 5000 all passed. To run: echo 200 | python3 /workspace/solution.py

No further action required.
